data.description: Presenting this Cullers Home resale: a 4-bed, 3-bath haven with a kitchen designed for culinary enthusiasts. Revel in a 36' cooktop, direct hood vent, hidden control dishwasher, and a sleek stainless steel pot filler. Seamless indoor-outdoor living is facilitated by expansive sliding patio doors.  Noteworthy is the home's pioneering energy advantage package, which remarkably reduces energy consumption by 40%, surpassing Energy Star ratings. This Cullers Home is an architectural masterpiece that seamlessly blends luxury, functionality, and sustainability, offering a truly exceptional living experience.
